reviewText:
Christmas gift for my grandson who has developed an interest in the Titanic. The video is a big hit with him.
I recommend it for the information provided and quality of the  production.
Good value.
I have a copy of the dvd that came with it .
From start to finish these dvds well set your mind straight onwhat really happened to the Titanic cruise liner., no movie fillers here.
A very thorough review of the process that led through the building of the ship and its subsequent demise on the ice berg.
